name: Sarika Halande
text: This is the fastest car i have ever drove, and with the best sound

name: Manthan Halande
text: This car is nothing less than a beast, its the craziest car i have ever drove

name: James C.
text: I've owned Aston Martins and Bentleys. The Obsidian is in a different league. The silence at 180km/h is eerie.

name: Elena R.
text: Visceral. That's the only word. It demands your attention every second.

name: Marcus T.
text: The hybrid transition is seamless. My only complaint is the waiting list for service appointments.

name: Alexander P.
text: It terrifies me. I love it.
